value:
Won't forgive... Never forgive...
The enemy... Yes, my enemy is...
Everyone...$k$pI will kill them...
I will kill all of them...

All the blame...lies with that person...
For Mother. For my brother. For the
Hoshidan soldiers.$k$pI will not...forgive...

Why are we standing around? Let's
go to battle. Kill...the enemy... That is
the key...

Where is it... Yes... My bow... My
precious bow...$k$pIt looks...different... But as long as it
can kill...

I must...protect Hoshido...along with
everyone. Ryoma, Hinoka, Sakura...
And...who else? Can't...remember...

I came here on
$Nf's order.
You don't seem to be my enemy...
With this... I can kill them all...
Won't be stopped...
Tsk...

Yes... Power... I need more...to
decimate them all...

Where am I? I am... Yes... Yes, I am
here to...defeat them... I must.

What are you doing here,
$Nu? It's time
for battle. The enemy... Must die.$k$pWhy...do I fight? Because I must... I
hear the anger inside me welling up,
shouting for me to fight.$k$pYes... Anger... I cannot forgive...my
enemy! Abandoning us siblings...
Abandoning our kingdom...$k$pThat person is my enemy. I must...
Kill... That's why I... When I jumped
from the wall, I... I couldn't be saved...$k$pI was...beyond saving... But if I wasn't
saved... How am I here? What...am I?
It doesn't matter. None of it matters.$k$pI must defeat...my enemy... That is all
that drives me!
あああっ！
Die...
うああっ！
You're in my way!
You're full of yourself!
Die, die, die!
I'll kill you myself.
I will kill my enemies.
I will... I must…
ふん…
Where am I? I can't remember anything...
Do you want to be the first to die?
Kill... Must kill them. But who?
I can hear that song. Azura?
Corrin... Ugh. My head, it hurts.
I just want to spend time with my family...
Until my memories return... I will kill all your enemies.
Hm.
I'll do it.
Die.
